{
  "stem": "4247.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I know everything now, right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my grandmother said, [SLOVAK]?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "OK, I mean, if you know everything, here's your rucksack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Go out and earn your living, and prove it to me, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So Emery was put out in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He lasted a few hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He came back and he said, I suppose I-- I-- I ought to continue studying.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that was the mentality at the time regarding these bourgeois middle class, lower middle class families, who were-- where the parents made a supreme effort to educate their children.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And what was your mother like?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I-- I do remember elementary school quite well, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to a school, which was also a state school near to where we lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in the Alzbet Street, Elizabeth Street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was-- it was, again, a fairly, you know, fairly competitive [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] school on its own level, of course.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember very clearly, and that is again rather-- rather-- rather characteristic to the times, of course we were living in the early-- after the first war-- irredentistic times.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at this early stage, they have instilled into us the injustice which happened to Hungary after being-- it has been dismembered after the First World War.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on one occasion we went to see-- the school took out-- took us out to see [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] such a play.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after the play we were assigned the duty of writing about the play, the way we felt about the play.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I, of course, like, was a particularly impressionable young boy.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
